---
import PageLayout from "../../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="In the News - Visualize the Data" currentPage="visualize">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="mb-6">
      <a href="/visualize" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-focus flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
        Back to Visualizations
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">In the News</h1>
    </div>
    
    <p class="mb-8 text-lg max-w-xl">
      Explore news articles and media coverage related to the data. This section provides context and contemporary perspectives on the events and patterns in our dataset.
    </p>

    <!-- Placeholder Content -->
    <div class="grid gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="p-6 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Coming Soon</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          The "In the News" section is currently under development. This page will feature:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li>Curated news articles related to the dataset</li>
          <li>Media coverage analysis and trends</li>
          <li>Historical context and contemporary perspectives</li>
          <li>Interactive filtering and search capabilities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Sample News Article</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">December 15, 2023 • The New York Times</p>
          <h4 class="font-medium">Sample Headline: Understanding Historical Patterns</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            This is a placeholder for a news article that would provide context and analysis related to the data in our collection. 
            The actual content will be populated with real news articles and media coverage.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-focus text-sm font-medium">Read full article →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">About This Section</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        The "In the News" section will provide contemporary context for the historical data, helping researchers and visitors understand 
        how these events were reported and perceived in their time, as well as their ongoing relevance today.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout> 